\par Marilyn:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid857456\charrsid857456 But it was secondary in another sense. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
