\par Marilyn:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid857456\charrsid857456 Yeah. And that, actually, was the most important thing, most important dimension to the whole exercise. I hadn\rquote 
t collected it myself. Despite my own initial experience, I deliberately did not collect fresh data. That was quite deliberate. I thought, \'93
What is here has a certain coherence. It was collected under certain conditions. If now, in writing this book, I then go and supplement it, it alters those conditions, whereas the conditions of collection, at least I can specify\'94. }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid857456\charrsid857456 
