nd I didn\rquote t know this, so I think it\rquote s apt to bring it in here, because I was going to ask you about this off record, but I think it\rquote s okay to bring it in - because I didn\rquote t realise it\rquote 
s a kind of autobiographical [reflection on] Kinship at the Core, something to that effect. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid857456\charrsid857456 
